AUDIO: 'We\'ll walk through how to use text prompts in the advanced editor to adjust lighting across the environment. [music] To get started, simply type the lighting changes you want in the prompt box. This is especially useful if you\'re aiming for softer, more ambient lighting'

[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'without harsh shadows. Reducing strong shadows makes it easier to place 3D models into the environment and have them blend naturally. You can adjust the outdoor environment as well. Any changes you make will automatically [music] influence the indoor lighting. The same'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
